205
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:52,620
Your Majesty, that's natural for you to do so.

206
00:13:52,860 --> 00:13:53,620
However, the people of Yongzhou

207
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:54,980
shouldn't be implicated

208
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,020
