320
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:43,180
Yes, I do.

321
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:45,060
What?

322
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:45,740
Although I don't know

323
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:47,260
how exactly things are going on between you guys,

324
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:47,940
I feel like

325
