00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:53,620
(Excellence, azure)

491
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:56,780
(If)

492
00:25:58,460 --> 00:25:59,020
(As well)

493
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,180
(Forever)

