538
00:29:11,460 --> 00:29:12,660
I guess

539
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:14,980
it's her retribution.

540
00:29:15,540 --> 00:29:16,940
Now that you put it like this,

541
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:19,380
